[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服<br />\n「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"262bc6f3470c8f1c261a555dff08c63fdc9c82b6","tid":1846963,"uid":314682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:17:24.000Z","msg":"me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929c16dc28aacec2a8f7a0260122f96c749b6702","tid":1846963,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beadf762a0b1d8cdd851ec46a5d538a32735f479","tid":1846963,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb55bdda909731e684303e887d9c43f6674dfe0f","tid":1846963,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57f3dcfeef7966a5f1e80756ca0fd4fa03e4e205","tid":1846963,"uid":206441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:07:37.000Z","msg":"我都係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:08:24.000Z","msg":"想像唔到社會會點樣平靜返...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:14:54.000